stein G, Bechara A, Damasio H, Damasio A | doi = 10.1111/j.0956-7976.2005.01553.x|pmid=15943668 |doi-broken-date=2020-03-06 }}\n* {{cite journal|title=Neuroanatomical correlates of brainstem coma |journal=Brain | volume = 126|pages=1524\u20131536|year=2003|vauthors=Parvizi J, Damasio AR |doi=10.1093/brain/awg166|pmid=12805123|issue=Pt 7}}\n* {{cite journal|title=Consciousness and the brainstem |journal=Cognition | volume = 79|pages=135\u2013160|year=2001|vauthors=Parvizi J, Damasio AR |doi=10.1016/S0010-0277(00)00127-X|pmid=11164026|issue=1\u20132|url=https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/1986213be8d88ebdaba7f91df50d783ca326e881 }}\n* {{cite journal|title=Subcortical and cortical brain activity during the feeling of self-generated emotions|journal=Nature Neuroscience | volume = 3|pages=1049\u20131056|year=2000|vauthors=Damasio AR, Grabowski TJ, Bechara A, Damasio H, Ponto LL, Parvizi J, Hichwa RD |doi=10.1038/79871|pmid=11017179|issue=10|url=https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/a1b487f1009a065b305eb22cf30f75eda5a15af6 }}\n* {{cite journal |title=How the brain creates the mind|journal=Scientific American | volume = 281|pages=74\u201379|year=1999|author= Damasio AR. |doi=10.1038/scientificamerican1299-112 |pmid=10614073 |issue=6|bibcode=1999SciAm.281f.112D }}\n* {{cite journal|title=Investigating the biology of consciousness |journal= Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society of London. Series B: Biological Sciences| volume = 353|issue=1377 |pages=1879\u20131882|year=1998|author= Damasio AR|doi=10.1098/rstb.1998.0339|pmid=9854259 |pmc=1692416}}\n* {{cite journal|title=Deciding advantageously before knowing the advantageous strategy|journal=Science | volume = 275|pages=1293\u20131294|year=1997|vauthors=Bechara A, Damasio H, Tranel D, Damasio AR |doi=10.1126/science.275.5304.1293|issue=5304|pmid=9036851}}\n* {{cite journal|title=The somatic marker hypothesis and the possible functions of the prefrontal cortex|journal=Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Societ